WEBVTT

00:02.420 --> 00:06.290
<b><i>This little light I've found</i></b>

00:08.610 --> 00:12.760
<b><i>Take it in, breathe it out</i></b>

00:15.160 --> 00:19.080
<b><i>A little drum that's beating loud</i></b>

00:21.480 --> 00:25.570
<b><i>In my chest, I hear the sound</i></b>

00:31.220 --> 00:33.750
<b><i>I can feel</i></b>

00:33.750 --> 00:36.200
<b><i>Feel you now</i></b>

00:36.200 --> 00:39.080
<b><i>I can feel you now</i></b>

00:39.080 --> 00:40.930
<b><i>I can feel</i></b>

00:41.890 --> 00:44.980
<b><i>I can feel you now</i></b>

01:27.520 --> 01:28.700
<b>Wallace.</b>

02:47.570 --> 02:52.710
<b>I knew that one day 
you would return to my side,</b>

02:54.360 --> 02:59.170
<b>Black Lotus, my angel.</b>

03:00.240 --> 03:02.660
<b>This is a blessing.</b>

03:03.350 --> 03:06.570
<b>It's not often that one gets 
to talk to their creator.</b>

03:07.500 --> 03:10.380
<b>Much less a creator, to his creation.</b>

03:15.170 --> 03:16.260
<b>Why?</b>

03:17.870 --> 03:19.790
<b>Why did you do this to me?</b>

03:21.320 --> 03:22.830
<b>Why me?</b>

03:28.960 --> 03:34.400
<b>You seek answers that might give 
your life definition, or meaning.</b>

03:35.230 --> 03:38.410
<b>That search is what makes us human.</b>

03:43.570 --> 03:47.180
<b>You are everything that I wanted you to be.</b>

03:47.870 --> 03:53.290
<b>I created you, gave you life and
 presented you with special gifts.</b>

03:53.290 --> 03:56.010
<b>You are the totality of my vision.</b>

03:57.050 --> 04:01.170
<b>Call it grand design, call it destiny.</b>

04:01.170 --> 04:03.770
<b>And you trying to kill me,</b>

04:03.770 --> 04:06.260
<b>is that part of your grand design?</b>

04:06.780 --> 04:10.270
<b>But everything I experienced, these memories,</b>

04:10.820 --> 04:14.390
<b>they're mine and only mine.</b>

04:16.210 --> 04:18.620
<b>You may be my creator,</b>

04:20.420 --> 04:23.020
<b>but you can't take them away from me.</b>

04:23.400 --> 04:26.210
<b>You were never meant to live forever.</b>

04:26.210 --> 04:29.830
<b>I'm certain your long journey has taken a toll.</b>

04:29.830 --> 04:34.200
<b>You are tired, hurt, broken.</b>

04:35.310 --> 04:38.080
<b>Soon you will be free to rest.</b>

04:43.630 --> 04:47.880
<b>A creation cannot be allowed 
to defy its creator.</b>

04:49.430 --> 04:53.860
<b>I made you to clear a path for me,</b>

04:55.070 --> 04:58.220
<b>to be my angel of death.</b>

04:58.940 --> 05:01.900
<b>I only wish that you could stay with me.</b>

05:03.570 --> 05:08.650
<b>But there's only room in my heart for one.</b>

05:19.900 --> 05:23.550
<b>And now I can witness a clash 
between my two greatest creations...</b>

08:49.210 --> 08:51.590
<b>Well, now it's clear what you two are after.</b>

08:56.180 --> 08:58.650
<b>The old Tyrell Archives.</b>

08:59.420 --> 09:02.990
<b>I've spent the last two years 
pouring over their files.</b>

09:05.310 --> 09:09.700
<b>In the future, the present 
species of humans will perish.</b>

09:13.840 --> 09:15.750
<b>But in the world that follows,</b>

09:15.750 --> 09:18.140
<b>my creations will rise to prominence...</b>

09:18.140 --> 09:20.870
<b>Spreading my glory across the earth,</b>

09:21.400 --> 09:23.720
<b>and then the stars.</b>

09:28.750 --> 09:32.040
<b>Mankind's fate is set in stone.</b>

09:36.840 --> 09:42.350
<b>So you wanna play God?</b>

10:23.420 --> 10:24.450
<b>J?</b>

10:25.050 --> 10:26.000
<b>Elle?</b>

10:27.340 --> 10:29.540
<b>I was wrong about you.</b>

10:32.880 --> 10:34.310
<b>Black Lotus!</b>

10:38.770 --> 10:40.780
<b>I'm not done with you.</b>

12:41.380 --> 12:43.300
<b>My water lily.</b>

12:44.290 --> 12:48.230
<b>So loyal, so pure.</b>

12:49.970 --> 12:55.520
<b>Yet ultimately, flawed.</b>

13:23.950 --> 13:28.500
<b>I can teach you to be the better angel.</b>

13:47.770 --> 13:49.780
<b>You cannot hurt me.</b>

13:49.780 --> 13:52.560
<b>You were designed as such.</b>

13:52.560 --> 13:56.530
<b>Come home and I can offer 
you what no one else can:</b>

13:57.240 --> 13:59.290
<b>your creator's love.</b>

14:08.650 --> 14:09.440
<b>Elle...</b>

14:50.060 --> 14:52.620
<b>Never forget the last thing you saw.</b>

14:54.320 --> 14:55.340
<b>J?</b>

15:04.020 --> 15:06.870
<b>Elle... I'm sorry.</b>

15:07.720 --> 15:09.090
<b>Forgive me.</b>

15:13.160 --> 15:14.450
<b>Save your strength.</b>

15:16.690 --> 15:18.350
<b>I failed.</b>

15:22.090 --> 15:24.730
<b>I forgot what really matters...</b>

15:27.190 --> 15:28.970
<b>I kept hurting you.</b>

15:31.490 --> 15:33.660
<b>Tried to make up for it.</b>

15:34.100 --> 15:37.830
<b>No. None of that matters to me.</b>

15:38.620 --> 15:41.000
<b>I still have good memories.</b>

15:42.400 --> 15:44.020
<b>And they're about you.</b>

15:47.470 --> 15:49.520
<b>You have a soul.</b>

15:50.720 --> 15:52.830
<b>You're more human than I am.</b>

15:59.510 --> 16:01.300
<b>J, don't talk.</b>

16:02.380 --> 16:05.650
<b>The detonator's... in the case.</b>

16:15.120 --> 16:15.870
<b>Wallace...</b>

16:43.670 --> 16:44.840
<b>Wait.</b>

16:57.210 --> 16:59.510
<b>J? J!</b>

17:00.890 --> 17:01.530
<b>J?</b>

17:04.030 --> 17:05.260
<b>Don't!</b>

17:07.920 --> 17:10.160
<b>J? J!</b>

17:20.210 --> 17:21.340
<b>J.</b>

18:06.800 --> 18:10.150
<b>Only you could go out on 
suspension, then get shot.</b>

18:10.780 --> 18:12.480
<b>It was just a stabbing.</b>

18:12.930 --> 18:14.540
<b>Don't exaggerate.</b>

18:15.560 --> 18:17.600
<b>Good to have you back, Davis.</b>

18:17.600 --> 18:20.200
<b>Try not to make any more trouble, rookie.</b>

18:20.470 --> 18:23.530
<b>Oh, I know. 
Next time, there won't be any trouble.</b>

18:47.220 --> 18:49.890
<b><i>But Mr. Wallace, there are serious 
concerns about the direction</i></b>

18:49.890 --> 18:52.130
<b><i>of the corporation, 
from both inside and outside.</i></b>

18:52.130 --> 18:56.810
<b><i>With the unfortunate passing 
of your father and now your--</i></b>

18:56.020 --> 18:59.880
<b>I'm not denying the issue with my health.</b>

19:01.010 --> 19:04.370
<b>But I assure you, I am still very much in charge.</b>

19:04.970 --> 19:09.610
<b>And I expect you all to remind everyone of that.</b>

19:10.160 --> 19:11.790
<b><i>But Mr. Wallace--</i></b>

19:10.970 --> 19:13.670
<b>Make sure that you don't forget, either.</b>

19:25.150 --> 19:27.340
<b>I see nothing</b>

19:29.860 --> 19:34.550
<b>but limitless possibilities.</b>

19:43.850 --> 19:44.740
<b>J?</b>

19:52.990 --> 19:53.800
<b>J?</b>

20:07.200 --> 20:08.380
<b>I see...</b>

21:04.110 --> 21:06.890
<b><i>Come along fast a little more</i></b>

21:06.890 --> 21:09.590
<b><i>Don't keep pushing me further</i></b>

21:09.590 --> 21:12.200
<b><i>Shining in the darkness on my own</i></b>

21:12.200 --> 21:15.050
<b><i>But baby I'm a real quick learner</i></b>

21:15.050 --> 21:17.640
<b><i>Thought that you could break me</i></b>

21:17.640 --> 21:20.510
<b><i>But I can never break so easy</i></b>

21:20.510 --> 21:24.570
<b><i>Believe me, it's about 
to get real, real messy</i></b>

21:25.260 --> 21:29.690
<b><i>Just know I learned the hard way</i></b>

21:29.690 --> 21:32.440
<b><i>It's getting turned into another way</i></b>

21:32.440 --> 21:34.680
<b><i>Now I'm numb to everything</i></b>

21:34.680 --> 21:40.250
<b><i>The highs have changed, started to flirt</i></b>

21:40.250 --> 21:42.780
<b><i>Thought you had my number</i></b>

21:42.780 --> 21:45.370
<b><i>But the tables have turned</i></b>

21:45.370 --> 21:48.410
<b><i>There's ice in my veins</i></b>

21:48.410 --> 21:50.700
<b><i>Nothing me can hurt me</i></b>

21:50.700 --> 21:53.340
<b><i>Now I feel no pain</i></b>

21:53.340 --> 21:56.020
<b><i>They won't see me coming</i></b>

